# LLM strategy documents

The `LLM/` directory contains strategy and architecture notes about the
AI/prompt/gateway logic. These are also exposed via the `sajtmaskin-mpc`
MCP server as `docs://local/llm/*`.

## Key files

- `LLM/AC-schema.txt` - Acceptance criteria for AI/gateway logic
- `LLM/v0-prompt-guide.txt` - v0 prompt best practices
- `LLM/DEPS-STATUS.txt` - Dependency versions and known issues
- `LLM/schemas_overview.txt` - API call schemas overview

## When to consult

Read these when changing AI/gateway/prompt-assist logic. After making
such changes, update the relevant LLM/ files to keep them in sync.
